%nav.navbar.navbar-custom.navbar-fixed-top{:role => "navigation"}
  .container-fluid
    .navbar-header
      %button.navbar-toggle{"data-target" => ".navbar-main-collapse", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :type => "button"}
        %i.fa.fa-bars
      %a.navbar-brand.page-scroll{:href => "#page-top"}
    .collapse.navbar-collapse.navbar-right.navbar-main-collapse
      %ul.nav.navbar-nav
        %li
          %a.page-scroll{:href => "#page-top"} Home
        %li
          %a.page-scroll{:href => "#about"} About
        %li
          %a.page-scroll{:href => "#our-work"} Our Work
        %li
          %a.page-scroll{:href => "#contact"} Contact
%header.intro
  .intro-body
    .container-fluid
      .row
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          %h1.brand-heading Cottonwood Coding
          %p.intro-text
            We build AWESOME custom websites from the ground up.
            %br
          %a.btn.btn-circle.page-scroll{:href => "#about"}
            %i.fa.fa-angle-double-down.animated
%section#about.container-fluid.content-section.text-center
  .row
    .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
      %h2 About Cottonwood Coding
      %p
        It all started with a Facebook post from our Co-Founder Dave Jungst...A single informative post about: templated, unsecured, non-responsive, poor SEO websites. Cottonwood Coding builds awesome, responsive, completely custom websites from the ground up. We provide the most secure, scalable, websites using the most up to date technologies and design techniques. We keep you involved every step of the way building the product that you want, allowing you to view changes and updates before your site goes live. Cottonwood Coding not only does amazing custom websites, we also offer complete software consulting. Contact us today for a free quote!
      %a.btn.btn-circle.page-scroll{:href => "#our-work"}
        %i.fa.fa-angle-double-down.animated
%section.content-section.text-center.container-fluid
  #our-work.our-work-section.row
    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
      %h2 Our Work
      #carousel-example-generic.carousel.slide{"data-ride" => "carousel"}
        .carousel-inner
          .item.active
            %a{href: 'http://www.hogstock.com', target: '_blank'}
              %img{:alt => "...", :src => image_path('hogstock-screen.png')}
                .carousel-caption
          .item
            %a{href: 'http://www.jscutah.com', target: '_blank'}
              %img{:alt => "...", :src => image_path('jsc-screen.png')}
                .carousel-caption
          .item
            %a{href: 'http://www.moonlightgardensupply.com', target: '_blank'}
              %img{:alt => "...", :src => image_path('moonlight-screen.png')}
                .carousel-caption
        %a.left.carousel-control{"data-slide" => "prev", :href => "#carousel-example-generic", :role => "button"}
          %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-left
        %a.right.carousel-control{"data-slide" => "next", :href => "#carousel-example-generic", :role => "button"}
          %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-right
      %a.btn.btn-circle.page-scroll{:href => "#contact"}
        %i.fa.fa-angle-double-down.animated
%section#contact.container-fluid.content-section.text-center
  .row
    .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
      %h2 Contact Us
      %p Feel free to email us to provide some feedback.
      %p
        %a{:href => "mailto:feedback@cottonwoodcoding.com"} feedback@cottonwoodcoding.com
      %ul.list-inline.banner-social-buttons
        %li
          %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{:href => "https://facebook.com/cottonwoodcoding", target: '_blank'}
            %i.fa.fa-facebook.fa-fw
            %span.network-name Facebook
        %li
          %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{:href => "https://twitter.com/cottonwoodcoding", target: '_blank'}
            %i.fa.fa-twitter.fa-fw
            %span.network-name Twitter
        %li
          %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{:href => "https://github.com/cottonwoodcoding", target: '_blank'}
            %i.fa.fa-github.fa-fw
            %span.network-name Github
%footer
  .container.text-center
    %p Copyright &copy; Cottonwood Coding 2014
    %a.btn.btn-circle.page-scroll{:href => "#page-top"}
      %i.fa.fa-angle-double-up.animated
